@NODE PROB "Known problems"

These are the known problems and bugs that I've found in this version, and that will hopefully fixed in the next ones.
If you have found any bug not listed here, contact me!

- Fullscreen mode shows some slight graphical glitches due to a problem with palette allocation. I've contacted the author of the SDL
library to see what could be the cause of this, I hope to fix this and release a new version, in the meanwhile I've kept the
fullscreen mode as some of you could not mind about these glitches.

- At startup there's a slight corruption of the graphics, which disappears shortly after.

- On my keyboard it's not possible to move and shoot at the same time when keeping down the slowdown key, might be related
to my keyboard.


